omething\'s wrong. %2$s. Please click the button above to retrieve a new Access Token.%3$s'=>'%1$sOh No something\'s wrong. %2$s. Please click the button above to retrieve a new Access Token.%3$s','%1$sLogin and Get my Access Token%2$s'=>'%1$sLogin and Get my Access Token%2$s','Feed Margin %1$sTo center feed type auto%2$s'=>'Feed Margin %1$sTo center feed type auto%2$s','Photos'=>'Photos','of'=>'of','View more for this Album'=>'View more for this Album','View Album'=>'View Album','Page Title Size'=>'Page Title Size','h6'=>'h6','h5'=>'h5','h4'=>'h4','h3'=>'h3','h2'=>'h2','h1 (Default)'=>'h1 (Default)','Heart and Comment counts only work when using Feed Type: Business Feed.'=>'Heart and Comment counts only work when using feed type: Business feed.','Responsive Gallery'=>'Responsive Gallery','Business Feed'=>'Business feed','Basic Feed'=>'Basic feed','Instagram Business Access Token'=>'Instagram Business access token','Instagram Basic Access Token'=>'Instagram Basic access token','Add your hashtag below. <strong>DO NOT</strong> add the #, just the name. Only one hashtag allowed at this time. Hashtag media only stays on Instagram for 24 hours and the API does not give us a date/time. In order to use the Instagram hashtag feed you must have your Instagram account linked to a Facebook Business Page. <a target="_blank" href="https://www.slickremix.com/docs/link-instagram-account-to-facebook/">Read Instructions.</a>'=>'Add your hashtag below. <strong>DO NOT</strong> add the #, just the name. Only one hashtag allowed at this time. Hashtag media only stays on Instagram for 24 hours and the API does not give us a date/time. In order to use the Instagram hashtag feed you must have your Instagram account linked to a Facebook Business Page. <a target="_blank" href="https://www.slickremix.com/docs/link-instagram-account-to-facebook/">Read Instructions.</a>','Top Media (Most Interactions)'=>'Top Media (Most Interactions)','Recent Media'=>'Recent Media','Hashtag Search Type'=>'Hashtag Search Type','Add your hashtag below. <strong>DO NOT</strong> add the #, just the name. Only one hashtag allowed at this time. Hashtag media only stays on Instagram for 24 hours and the API does not give us a date/time. That also means if you decide to combine this feed these media posts will appear before any other posts because we cannot sort them by date. In order to use the Instagram hashtag feed you must have your Instagram account linked to a Facebook Business Page. <a target="_blank" href="https://www.slickremix.com/docs/link-instagram-account-to-facebook/">Read Instructions.</a>'=>'Add your hashtag below. <strong>DO NOT</strong> add the #, just the name. Only one hashtag allowed at this time. Hashtag media only stays on Instagram for 24 hours and the API does not give us a date/time. That also means if you decide to combine this feed these media posts will appear before any other posts because we cannot sort them by date. In order to use the Instagram hashtag feed you must have your Instagram account linked to a Facebook Business Page. <a target="_blank" href="https://www.slickremix.com/docs/link-instagram-account-to-facebook/">Read Instructions.</a>','Feed Them Social - Page, Post, Video and Photo Galleries'=>'Feed Them Social - Page, Post, Video and Photo Galleries','No Tweets available. Login as Admin to see more details.'=>'No Tweets available. Login as Admin to see more details.','Picture from Facebook'=>'Picture from Facebook','Please update ALL Premium Extensions for Feed Them Social because they will no longer work with this version of Feed Them Social. We have made some Major Changes to the Core of the plugin to help with plugin conflicts. Please update your extensions from your <a href="https://www.slickremix.com/my-account" target="_blank">My Account</a> page on our website if you are not receiving notifications for updates on the premium extensions. Thanks again for using our plugin!'=>'Please update ALL Premium Extensions for Feed Them Social